data.description: First time ever on the market. Trust Sale needs TLC. Location, location…end of street on Canyon with views of Ocean & Sea World. Walk to Elementary & Pt Loma High School. Open kitchen with granite counter & stainless-steel appliances, custom rock fireplace in family room, beautiful custom-built patio with trellis off kitchen & lots of space to entertain. Unique outdoor built-in Pizza oven. Quieter homes program installed new windows & HVAC system. Plenty of parking with room for boat & RV. Workshop in garage. Large laundry room w/storage. Must see…lots of potential so bring your ideas.This home is ideal for expanding the square footage if you need a bigger home. Building a second story would give you panoramic ocean view of the coastline to Pacific Beach and on. Or you could add a deck to the existing home for entertaining areas off the living room and the master bedroom which would enhance the existing views. There are so many possibilities with this property with its secluded private location. You must come see it.
